The MGJ is a miniature sized version of the MGP standard guided actuator designed for small load applications that require high accuracy. Its integrated guide rods provides a non-rotating accuracy of +/-0.1&#xb0;. It is targeted for the electronic equipment and instrumentation industries and not intended for use in stopper applications.
